name: Steampunk
description:
This tune was born in 2010. 
Right after that I stopped working music for almost 12 years...
This track was never released officially, in those days I couldn't decide on which record label will be better to release it, mainly because "Steampunk" was the only one track I made in this music genre.
Now I'm back in business, developing other project.
Today I made an unusual decision...
There is only one FLAC on the Internet, it is in front of you.
There is only one copy.
And the price is so low that I can only raise a glass of good wine for its new owner, because after the purchase I completely waive any rights to own it.
"Steampunk" will be totally your creation.
On my YouTube channel there is video with it, which I added in 2011, in the comments to which I`ll write whatever you want: that you bought it, that you created it, and I posted it with your permission, that I refused any ownership and copyrights, or maybe if you like, I'll delete the video (at the moment it's a protection against attempts to make other copies).

I will be sincerely happy for you, my friend, I`m sure you will manage this awesome tune better than me.

I love this track, but sometimes we all need to let go of what we love.
